Sophia Edge Node -- Sound Effects
==================================

Place .wav sound files here for HUD overlay notifications.

Expected files:
  achievement_unlock.wav  -- Short chime for regular achievement unlocks
  mastery.wav             -- Longer fanfare for mastery/legendary achievements
  daily_summary.wav       -- Brief tone for daily digest notification

Format requirements:
  - WAV format (PCM, uncompressed)
  - 16-bit, mono or stereo
  - 22050 Hz or 44100 Hz sample rate
  - Keep files short (under 3 seconds for achievement, under 5 for mastery)
  - Small file size preferred (RPi storage is limited)

The HUD overlay will attempt playback via aplay (ALSA), paplay (PulseAudio),
or mpv in that order. If no audio player is available, notifications are
silent (text-only).

Installation:
  The install.sh script copies this directory to /opt/sophia-edge-node/sounds/
  on the target Raspberry Pi.
